rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome, mo! For the remote
Liberalitas, Yutayuta has
brought accessories, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Country folk should pay more attention
to fashion, mo! Yutayuta will not
forgive any frumpiness, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0003
rows.name:
You've made a good purchase,
mo! That should get rid of
the frumpiness, mo!

rows.label: tlk42450261_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Arararararararara, mo! Do you
prefer being frumpy, mo?
